text: Much better food here and local delight - experience old time kaki meetup and kopi time feeling. One of the best in Bkt Merah - Briyani really nice. *Better than those opp at SAFRA like the Delhi Curry one mentioned by someone above*. Best support local authentic SG mamak stalls.
Tapau for the family. The mutton briyani & egg masala thosai were pretty good. Rather understated restaurant.
Don't mind the table. It's clean actually but I accidentally spilled the water. The meals are roti prata  with kari kambing, rose milik syrup and katirah.

Second time coming here and not disappointed. Prata is one of the best and it comes with mutton curry!

Customer service is always the best here.

Cheap but amazingly delicious food, what else can you ask for?
They cook quality food with home made recipe..  friendly staff service
